1. It is used to join multiple strings with delimter
2. It is also used to join multiple strings with delimter and prefix and suffix.
3. It will have constructor like below
- public StringJoiner(String delimter)
- public StringJoiner (String delimter , String prefix , String suffix)
4. It is also used in Collectors.joining() code
- Collectors.joining() // no delimter
- Collectors.joining(String delimter)
- Collectors.joining(String delimter, String prefix , String suffix)
5. Some real life use cases
- Join list of emails string with comma separated
List<String> emails = List.of("email1","email2);

Do like below 
email1,email2 // String type variable
